"{\"uid\": \"pakistankakhudahafiz.com-touching-moments-when-the-olympic-hero-comes-back-to-mian-channu\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PKKH.tv A Pakistan centric depiction of the South Asian contemporary affairs PKKH.tv A Pakistan centric depiction of the South Asian contemporary affairs The 27-year-old Olympic gold champion was met with a hero's welcome upon her arrival at Lahore airport late on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.732237034139162e-20, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1874845695305408e-15, \"text\": \"South Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.732237034139162e-20, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 124, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1874845695305408e-15, \"text\": \"South Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 27-year-old Olympic gold champion\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"a hero's welcome\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"her arrival\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"Lahore airport\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday night\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was showered with praise from thousands of supporters and a police marching band before emerging into the terminal to further cheers.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"supporters\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"a police marching band\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"the terminal\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"further cheers\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A large group of government officials, including ministers and bureaucrats, greeted him, along with members of his family, including his father, who wore a garland around his neck.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A large group\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"government officials\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"ministers\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"bureaucrats\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 567}, {\"ngram\": \"a garland\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"his neck\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With dhol wallahs, dancing youths, and a police escort, he then set off in a procession to his ancestral house in Chak 101-15L.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dhol wallahs\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"dancing youths\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"a police escort\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"a procession\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"his ancestral house\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"Chak\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cavalcade that escorted him home took a lengthy and convoluted path over the renowned GT Road, making the two and a half-hour trip from Lahore take longer than six hours.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lahore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9294876467737056e-27, \"text\": \"Lahore\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lahore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lahore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cavalcade\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"a lengthy and convoluted path\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the renowned GT Road\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"the two and a half-hour trip\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"six hours\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People waited for hours along the roadway to catch a glimpse of the first-ever individual Olympic gold medalist in the history of the nation.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the roadway\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"a glimpse\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the first-ever individual Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's our son,\\\" we said.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our son\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A resident of Mian Chunnu told reporters along the road, \\\"[He] has given us real happiness after a long time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999730116546, \"rank\": 2.6957669922016313e-08, \"text\": \"Mian\", \"t